姆就曾参与剧本的同桌分角阅读<ref name="ewhamm">{{cite web | url = https://ew.com/movies/2017/06/20/baby-driver-jon-hamm/ | title = Jon Hamm opens up about his bank-robbing Baby Driver character | first = Clark | last = Collis | work = Entertainment Weekly | access-date = 2021-08-15 | date = 2017-06-20 | archive-date = 2021-02-11 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211202713/https://ew.com/movies/2017/06/20/baby-driver-jon-hamm/}}</ref>。
