== 制作 ==
=== 早期发展和准备 ===
[[File:Edgar_Wright_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg|thumb]]

赖特早在1995年就萌生本片构想，当时他21岁，住在[[伦敦|伦敦]]近郊，编剧和导演事业尚无起色，但一直对项目充满热情<ref name="Entcast" /><ref name="Bdguardian2" /><ref name="nypostbd">{{Cite web | url = https://nypost.com/2017/06/29/how-a-new-york-band-inspired-baby-driver-20-years-ago/ | title = How a New York band inspired 'Baby Driver' 20 years ago | last = Phull | first = Hardeep | date = 2017-06-29 | website = [[紐約郵報|New York Post]] | access-date = 2021-08-15 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014718/http://nypost.com/2017/06/29/how-a-new-york-band-inspired-baby-driver-20-years-ago/}}</ref>。他搬到伦敦拍摄职业电影处女作、低成本西部喜剧片《[[荒野大指客|荒野大指客]]》，同时思考未来在娱乐业如何发展<ref name="Entcast" />。赖特反复聆听[[乔恩·斯宾塞布鲁斯爆炸|乔恩·斯宾塞布鲁斯爆炸]]乐队第四张录音室《[[Orange_(乔恩·斯宾塞布鲁斯爆炸专辑)|Orange]]》，为构想《极盗车神》助力<ref name="Entcast" />。起初他的思路是高速追车，随后演变成完整桥段，逃逸司机在车上随歌曲《喇叭裤》起舞，接下来进入追车戏<ref name="nypostbd" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite web | archive-date = 2021-02-05 | access-date = 2021-08-15 | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-features/baby-driver-how-edgar-wright-staged-the-crime-movies-musical-action-scenes-252893/ | title = 'Baby Driver': How Edgar Wright Staged the Crime Movie's Musical Action Scenes | last = Fear | first = David | date = 2017-06-28 | website = Rolling Stone | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210205134803/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-features/baby-driver-how-edgar-wright-staged-the-crime-movies-musical-action-scenes-252893/}}</ref>。这场戏后来写入剧本放在电影开头，但赖特此时的构想才刚起步，距项目落实还差得远<ref name="Bdguardian2" />。电影定型时的艺术走向受众多因素影响，如[[IPod|iPod]]面世、赖特童年时的耳鸣症，他对[[奧利佛·薩克斯|奧利佛·薩克斯]]著作《[[音乐神经学|音乐神经学]]》的理解等<ref name=":0" />。

2003年赖特用2.5万英镑预算为[[尼尔·克拉克斯顿|尼尔·克拉克斯顿]]的《蓝歌》制作音乐视频，故事背景源自《极盗车神》早期构想<ref name="bdrt">{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | access-date = 2021-08-15 | url = https://www.roadandtrack.com/car-culture/profiles/a10318782/baby-driver-edgar-white-interview/ | title = Pursuit of Perfection | first = Max | last = Prince | date = 2017-07-21 | work = Road & Track | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411032005/https://www.roadandtrack.com/car-culture/profiles/a10318782/baby-driver-edgar-white-interview/}}</ref>。视频的成功出人意料，赖特对此很高兴，但他认为构想潜力远不止此，感到有些浪费<ref name="Bdguardian2" /><ref name="inspire">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-08-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181227131514/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2017/03/baby-driver-sxsw | url = https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2017/03/baby-driver-sxsw | title = Edgar Wright Makes a Triumphant Return at SXSW with Baby Driver | first = Joanna | last = Robinson | date = 2017-03-12 | work = [[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]] | archive-date = 2018-12-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。回首往事，赖特承认2003年的音乐视频意义重大，是《极盗车神》的[[概念验证|概念验证]]<ref name="Bdguardian2" />。赖特首部重要长片《[[活人甡吃|活人甡吃]]》（2004年）从艺术导向上看是催生《极盗车神》的重要催化剂，代表他开始长期同Working Title Films制片人合作，《极盗车神》前期发展离不开他们的协助<ref name="Entcast" />。2007年赖特已同Working Title签署拍摄多部电影的合约，心中对《极盗车神》已有明确构思，他与[[史蒂文·普赖斯|史蒂文·普赖斯]]会晤，探讨影片早期音乐理念<ref name="Entcast" />。剧本创作在2010年《[[歪小子史考特|歪小子史考特]]》上映前后开始，但赖特因项目《[[世界尽头_(电影)|世界尽头]]》（2013年）与《[[蟻人_(電影)|蚁人]]》分身-{乏}-术，其中《蚁人》此时项目前景未定，赖特已同[[喬·柯尼許|喬·柯尼許]]创作剧本，需要优先处理，故《极盗车神》的前期准备一再延迟<ref name="Entcast" />。赖特离开《蚁人》后立即投身本片制作，制片商在开拍前开始整理演员和技术人员名册<ref name="Entcast" />。赖特与洛杉矶、伦敦前职业罪犯共事，力求准确反映银行抢劫犯如何“工作”<ref name="bdrt" />。

赖特与首席剪辑[[保罗·马奇利斯|保罗·马奇利斯]]、洛杉矶剪辑埃文·希夫在制作初期用[[分鏡|动画分镜]]设计预剪辑草案。马奇利斯负责用Avid Media Composer软件把每个动画分镜与配乐歌曲切分，他和赖特曾在《世界尽头》和《歪小子斯科特对抗全世界》合作。马奇利斯还在片场提供摄制建议，这对剪辑师来说很不寻常。<ref name="frame">{{cite web | url = https://blog.frame.io/2017/07/31/baby-driver-workflow/ | title = The Missing Details of Baby Driver's Crazy Workflow | first = Ron | last = Dawson | website = Frame | access-date = 2021-08-15 | date = 2017-07-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210613001902/https://blog.frame.io/2017/07/31/baby-driver-workflow/ | archive-date = 2021-06-13 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 摄制 ===
[[File:Peachtree_Center_Entrance_Looking_West.jpg|thumb]]

《极盗车神》本以[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]为背景，但高昂的制作成本令剧组望而却步<ref name="bdrt" /><ref name="complex" />。制片商决定挑选为电影制作提供优厚可转移[[免税额度|免税额度]]的城市，[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]在选址侦探提供的选项中脱颖而出。该市大片出境率比其他全球城市高一倍，为确保剧情真实可信，镜头必须保留城市风貌。<ref name="complex" /><ref name="vice">{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-09-19 | access-date = 2021-08-16 | url = https://www.vice.com/en/article/gyp3qm/we-talked-to-director-edgar-wright-about-making-this-summers-best-movie | title = 'Baby Driver' Is This Summer's Most Adrenaline-Packed Action Movie | first = Amil | last = Niazi | date = 2017-06-19 | work = [[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]] | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200919071025/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/gyp3qm/we-talked-to-director-edgar-wright-about-making-this-summers-best-movie}}</ref>赖特用一周在亚特兰大了解地方景观和文化以便按需修改剧本，发现该城身为物流枢纽更适合《极盗车神》剧情落实<ref name="complex">{{cite web | url = https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2017/06/baby-driver-loves-atlanta | title = 'Baby Driver' Is a High Octane Love Letter to Atlanta | first = Justin | last = Davis | date = 2017-06-28 | work = Complex | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210725000405/https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2017/06/baby-driver-loves-atlanta | archive-date = 2021-07-25 | access-date = 2021-08-16}}</ref>。电影2016年2月开始[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]，耗时四个月，同年五月收尾<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-05-18 | url = https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/edgar-wright-s-baby-driver-1368671221891126.html | title = Edgar Wright's 'Baby Driver' Off and Running | first = Jen | last = Chaney | website = Yahoo! | date = 2016-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210518015706/https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/edgar-wright-s-baby-driver-1368671221891126.html | access-date = 2021-08-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-06-29 | url = https://collider.com/baby-driver-filming-edgar-wright/ | title = Baby Driver: Filming Wraps on Edgar Wright's New Film | date = 2016-05-16 | first = Adam | last = Chitwood | website = Collider | access-date = 2021-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200629104658/https://collider.com/baby-driver-filming-edgar-wright/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>，基本在[[亚特兰大市中心|亚特兰大市中心]]取景<ref name="complex" />。选址注重突出亚特兰大地标（如[[桃树中心|桃树中心]]）、文化机构乃至当地传媒<ref name="atlantamag">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-08-16 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.atlantamagazine.com/news-culture-articles/baby-driver-filming-locations-map/ | title = A map of all the places Baby Driver filmed in Atlanta | first = Matt | last = Walljasper | date = 2017-08-03 | work = Atlanta | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201208035649/https://www.atlantamagazine.com/news-culture-articles/baby-driver-filming-locations-map/ | archive-date = 2020-12-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-08-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200815101815/https://www.ajc.com/blog/buzz/things-love-about-atlanta-filmed-baby-driver/CTZPcZw2dgQPuwbgoWJhPI/ | title = 5 things we love about Atlanta-filmed 'Baby Driver' | url = https://www.ajc.com/blog/buzz/things-love-about-atlanta-filmed-baby-driver/CTZPcZw2dgQPuwbgoWJhPI/ | first = Jennifer | last = Brett | date = 2017-06-27 | work = Atlanta Journal-Constitution | publisher = Donna B. Hall | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-16}}</ref>。其他取景地点包括乔治亚州[[蓋恩斯維爾_(喬治亞州)|盖恩斯维尔]]与[[門羅縣_(喬治亞州)|门罗县]]乡村<ref name="atlantamag" />。选址侦探曾为第一摄制组探查亚特兰大其他郊区，但赖特觉得郊区茂密的树叶不适合充当本片背景，城市化的一面更好<ref name="bdrt" />。电影拍摄期间共为地方经济贡献3010万美元<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2017/06/22/georgia-filmed-baby-driver-contributed-30-1.html | title = Georgia-filmed 'Baby Driver' contributed $30.1 million to economy | first = Ellie | last = Hensley | date = 2017-06-22 | work = Atlanta Business Chronicle | access-date = 2021-08-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170905102453/https://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2017/06/22/georgia-filmed-baby-driver-contributed-30-1.html | archive-date = 2020-06-29}}</ref>。

赖特表示，《[[粉身碎骨_(1971年电影)|粉身碎骨]]》（1971年）、《[[美國風情畫|美國風情畫]]》（1973年）、《[[虎口拔牙|虎口拔牙]]》（1978年）、《[[驚爆點|驚爆點]]》（1991年）、《[[落水狗|落水狗]]》（1992年）、《[[盜火線|盜火線]]》（1995年）等电影对本片视觉特点和创作导向影响很大<ref name=":0" /><ref name="bdrt" /><ref name="inspire" /><ref name="atlantic">{{cite web | url = https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2017/07/baby-driver-is-a-rare-heist-movie-with-a-heart/532572/ | title = Baby Driver Is a Rare Heist Movie With a Heart | first = David | last = Sims | date = 2017-07-04 | work = [[大西洋_(雜誌)|The Atlantic]] | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210307103046/https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2017/07/baby-driver-is-a-rare-heist-movie-with-a-heart/532572/ | archive-date = 2021-03-07 | access-date = 2021-08-16}}</ref>。为营造美感，剧组的主要目标包括以实景电影制作技术拍摄<ref name="panavision">{{cite web | url = https://www.panavision.com/bill-popes-cinematography-baby-driver-has-panavision-under-hood | title = Bill Pope's Cinematography for Baby Driver Has Panavision Under the Hood | date = 2017-07-03 | website = [[潘那维申|Panavision]] | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-11-25 | access-date = 2021-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201125083400/https://www.panavision.com/bill-popes-cinematography-baby-driver-has-panavision-under-hood}}</ref>。这需要精心策划来协调特技和编舞，尽可能[[镜头内剪辑|都用镜头拍出来]]，实在不得以才动用[[视觉效果|视觉效果]]<ref name="artofvfx">{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-01-18 | url = https://www.artofvfx.com/baby-driver-stuart-lashley-vfx-supervisor-double-negative/ | title = Baby Driver: Stuart Lashley – VFX Supervisor – Double Negative | first = Vincent | last = Frei | date = 2017-09-19 | website = Art of VFX | access-date = 2021-08-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210118063822/http://www.artofvfx.com/baby-driver-stuart-lashley-vfx-supervisor-double-negative/}}</ref><ref name="thrstunt">{{cite web | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/baby-driver-stunt-coordinator-we-tried-do-everything-camera-1017348/ | title = 'Baby Driver' Stunt Coordinator: 'We Tried to Do Everything in Camera' | first = Carolyn | last = Giardina | date = 2017-06-29 | work = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210220053510/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/baby-driver-stunt-coordinator-we-tried-do-everything-camera-1017348 | access-date = 2021-08-16 | archive-date = 2021-02-20}}</ref>。《极盗车神》是摄影总监比尔·波普与赖特继《世界尽头》和《歪小子斯科特对抗全世界》后合作的第三部电影。波普基本是用宽银幕[[35毫米膠片|35毫米]]柯达胶片拍摄本片，采用潘那维申Panaflex Millennium XL2摄像机配备G、T、C系列宽银幕镜头<ref name="panavision" />。为捕捉激烈特技或达成导演为个别镜头要求的特殊摄制角度，摄影师还需以专用相机配合[[超级35|超级35]]胶片拍摄<ref name="dneg">{{cite web | url = https://www.digitalmediaworld.tv/in-depth/1643-double-negative-puts-pedal-to-the-metal-for-baby-driver | title = Double Negative Puts Pedal to the Metal for 'Baby Driver' | first = Adriene | last = Hurst | publisher = Digital Media World | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201205092608/https://digitalmediaworld.tv/in-depth/1643-double-negative-puts-pedal-to-the-metal-for-baby-driver | archive-date = 2020-12-05 | access-date = 2021-08-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。物流运输遇到困难之际，[[潘那维申|潘那维申]]驻亚特兰大办事处协调剧组满足摄制需要<ref name="panavision" />。高潮戏在[[亞特蘭大獵鷹|亞特蘭大獵鷹]]训练设施停车场上演，剧组只能夜间借用拍摄，灯光昏暗导致摄制非常困难<ref name="panavision" />。最后剧组采用翻新后[[曝光宽容度|曝光宽容度]]更大的[[阿萊Alexa|阿萊Alexa]]相机以数字格式拍摄<ref name="frame" /><ref name="panavision" />。

=== 视觉效果 ===
赖特注重实效电影制作手段，片中视觉特效很少<ref name="saveaction">{{cite news | last = O'Falt | first = Chris | title = 'Baby Driver': How Edgar Wright Is Saving the Action Film | archive-date = 2020-11-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109005053/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/06/baby-driver-edgar-wright-interview-action-film-1201848230/ | access-date = 2021-08-16 | website = [[IndieWire|IndieWire]] | date = 2017-06-29 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.indiewire.com/2017/06/baby-driver-edgar-wright-interview-action-film-1201848230/}}</ref>。斯图尔特·拉什利与谢兰德拉·斯旺卡监督伦敦[[双重否定_(视觉特效工作室)|双重否定]]特效公司创作本片大部分视觉效果<ref name="artofvfx" />，共计430个镜头<ref name="dneg" />，投入专业画师120人<ref name="artofvfx" />。他们以电影早期动画分镜为参考确定视听项目<ref name="dneg" />，使用[[Nuke|Nuke]]软件制作无法直接用镜头拍摄的追车动画。追车桥段一旦重拍往往就需要更新特效动画，特效组需维护软件控制工具，以便画师随时调用最新音频。<ref name="dneg" />英国莫里奈公司也为本片制作特效镜头<ref name="dneg" />。

据拉什利透露，突出电影视听组合曲目的关键桥段包括“哈莱姆曳步舞”、宝贝走街串巷买咖啡的[[推軌鏡頭|推轨单镜头]]、“龙舌兰酒”、道哥抢劫团伙与卧底警察交火。“哈莱姆曳步舞”是片中比较复杂的桥段，剧组拍摄并保留的镜头量超出所需，以便需要时调用。<ref name="dneg" />“龙舌兰酒”桥段布景需要精确配合镜头内剪辑。双重否定用子弹发射、火花、枪声补充真人镜头，同时牢记配合音乐鼓点节奏<ref name="dneg" />。特效工作组发现镜头融合音频对真人电影非常适合，但如何向观众传达情感暗示等问题对工作提出独特挑战<ref name="dneg" />。

《极盗车神》的高潮桥段称为“布莱顿摇滚”，为保障安全、避免损失太大，双重否定用计算机生成画面强化镜头。为体现车辆撞到人物，特效组分阶段制作事故画面，再融合成完整镜头，营造现实感和控制感。<ref name="dneg" />巴迪偷来的警车从停车场顶楼坠落中庭，剧组需缩短掉落距离，在停车场另一边用起重机按车主要求把车放下。双重否定用中庭的[[光学雷达|光学雷达]]扫描图接景，叠加特技延长实际坠落时间。<ref name="dneg" />

=== 特技与编舞 ===
第二摄制组导演达林·普雷斯科特、特技司机杰里米·弗莱及其他专家组成的团队协调影片车辆特效<ref name="Entstunts">{{cite web | url = https://ew.com/movies/2017/07/02/baby-driver-cars-stunts/ | title = Quite a few cars were broken in the making of Baby Driver | first = Clark | last = Collis | work = Entertainment Weekly | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210214020759/https://ew.com/movies/2017/07/02/baby-driver-cars-stunts/ | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-16 | date = 2017-07-02 | archive-date = 2021-02-14}}</ref><ref name="Inversestunt">{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-07-29 | date = 2017-06-28 | work = Inverse | dead-url = no | url = https://www.inverse.com/article/33512-how-baby-driver-did-car-stunts-edgar-wright-george-miller-ansel-elgort | title = 'Mad Max' and Matchbox Cars Helped 'Baby Driver' Nail Its Crazy Stunts | first = Jordan | last = Zakarin | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210729190145/https://www.inverse.com/article/33512-how-baby-driver-did-car-stunts-edgar-wright-george-miller-ansel-elgort}}</ref>。他们取得市区拍摄许可前先在[[亚特兰大赛车场|亚特兰大赛车场]]排练，剧组用特制的起重机镜头、装有起重机臂且内置摄像机的小汽车捕捉特技。接下来马奇利斯把胶片剪成新版动画，及时提高特技拍摄精度。<ref name="Inversestunt" />许多车辆特技是弗莱开车，演员经过适当训练可以参与要求不高的特技演出<ref name="Cbc">{{cite web | url = https://www.cbc.ca/radio/day6/episode-345-north-korea-s-top-anchor-returns-baby-driver-s-best-stunts-finding-amelia-earhart-and-more-1.4192751/meet-the-stunt-driver-behind-baby-driver-s-crazy-car-chases-1.4192792 | title = Meet the stunt driver behind Baby Driver's crazy car chases | author = Staff | website = CBC Radio | access-date = 2020-11-12 | date = 2017-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023531/https://www.cbc.ca/radio/day6/episode-345-north-korea-s-top-anchor-returns-baby-driver-s-best-stunts-finding-amelia-earhart-and-more-1.4192751/meet-the-stunt-driver-behind-baby-driver-s-crazy-car-chases-1.4192792 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

《极盗车神》的特效演出非常复杂，普雷斯科特认为本片是他最重要的项目<ref name="thrstunt" />。片中“180度进、180度出”桥段由弗莱驾车高速通过多辆汽车阻挡的窄巷，其间车头与车尾对调位置（180度）。据普雷斯科特回忆，这场戏共拍摄五到六次，“你要考虑很多，不能让杰里米受伤，拍这场戏要花不少钱，摄影师需保持距离以免受伤”。<ref name="thrstunt" />电影片头的高速公路追逐戏也很复杂、难拍<ref name="Inversestunt" /><ref name="nytstunts">{{cite web | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/27/movies/baby-driver-stunts.html | title = How They Pulled Off the Perfectly Timed Stunts in 'Baby Driver' | first = Mekado | last = Murphy | work = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 2017-06-27 | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111212837/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/27/movies/baby-driver-stunts.html}}</ref>，剧组无权封闭[[85號州際公路|85號州際公路]]，必须在八小时内完成摄制，迫使众人仅排练一小时就在凌晨开拍。除多次高速跨越外，桥段还有跨越障碍物等特技，普雷斯科特带队一边考虑交通状况一边仔细协调。庞大的警方车队包围50辆电影摄制车，占满85号州际公路所有车道。<ref name="Inversestunt" />根据剧本要求，男主角驾驶的逃逸用车应该低调，容易融入周围车辆<ref name="nytstunts" />。赖特根据失窍汽车统计数据选中[[丰田卡罗拉|丰田卡罗拉]]，但制片商要求车辆“稍性感点儿”，剧组最后选用[[红色|红色]][[速霸陸Impreza|斯巴鲁WRX]]<ref name="nytstunts" />。

[[瑞安·赫芬顿|瑞安·赫芬顿]]负责本片编舞，确保片中编舞桥段电影演员和特技演员的动作同步<ref name="lachoreo">{{cite web | url = https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/la-et-ms-baby-driver-music-edgar-wright-danger-mouse-heffington-dance-moves-20170701-story.html | title = How Edgar Wright, Danger Mouse and choreographer Ryan Heffington gave 'Baby Driver' its perfect groove | first = Randall | last = Roberts | work = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 2017-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210704102737/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/la-et-ms-baby-driver-music-edgar-wright-danger-mouse-heffington-dance-moves-20170701-story.html | archive-date = 2021-07-04 | access-date = 2021-08-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《极盗车神》是他首次参与电影制作，此前主要同[[希雅|希雅]]、[[拱廊之火|拱廊之火]]等艺人合作，名声基本局限在音乐领域<ref name="lachoreo" />。赫芬顿觉得本片剧本引人入胜，但他不熟悉导演以往的作品，只能在首次面试后花时间补课<ref name="Entchoreo">{{cite web | url = https://ew.com/movies/2017/07/08/baby-driver-choreographer-ryan-heffington-ansel-elgort/ | title = How the choreographer of Baby Driver got Ansel Elgort to 'dance his ass off' | first = Clark | last = Collis | work = Entertainment Weekly | access-date = 2021-08-16 | date = 2017-07-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201213092043/https://ew.com/movies/2017/07/08/baby-driver-choreographer-ryan-heffington-ansel-elgort/ | archive-date = 2020-12-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。赫芬顿与赖特早期面谈时详细交流艺术视野，用节奏或结构充满戏剧变化的歌曲充当模板<ref name="lachoreo" />。赫芬顿在电影开拍第一天已经开始督导“哈莱姆曳步舞”桥段，现场聘用五到六十名[[臨時演員|臨時演員]]<ref name="Entchoreo" />。艾尔高特和福克斯都有舞蹈经验，所以其他桥段编舞没那么费劲儿<ref name="Entchoreo" />。演员排练每个桥段时都播放音乐，一个个镜头练习<ref name="dneg" />。

=== 音效设计 ===
[[File:Twickenham_Film_Studios.jpg|thumb]]

朱利安·斯莱特获邀参与项目前收到剧本副本和[[可移植文档格式|便携式文档]]，其中包含精心挑选的音乐和粗略[[混音|混音]]<ref name="indiesound" />。他与音乐编辑布拉德利·法默密切合作，把每段音乐分解成独特的[[节奏图|节奏图]]，进而满足任何时间的同步需求。为避免音乐响起时掉拍，他们经常需要[[音频变调|音频变调]]。<ref name="indiesound" />两人用不同音频模拟宝贝的[[耳鸣|耳鸣]]，有时效果明显，有时只可意味、难以言传。耳鸣强度取决于宝贝的情绪，越焦急声音越大。<ref name="indiesound" />事实证明音频节奏变化很难把握，斯莱特称，法默用实例表明，考虑每个音乐环节的同时，也要考虑没有音乐应该怎么处理，这样需要的构想时间就长得多<ref name="indiesound" />。“哈莱姆曳步舞”桥段的音效创作最复杂，经过25轮才处理好，其中既有发动机各种差异微妙的音效，又有变化细微的对白等<ref name="ibc">{{cite news | last = Stout | first = Andy | title = Under the bonnet of Baby Driver's sound design | url = https://www.ibc.org/trends/sculpting-the-sound-mix-of-edgar-wrights-baby-driver-/2166.article | website = IBC | date = 2017-08-23 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-16 | archive-date = 2021-04-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210410191146/https://www.ibc.org/trends/sculpting-the-sound-mix-of-edgar-wrights-baby-driver-/2166.article }}</ref>。“布莱顿摇滚”同样对剧组提出高要求，需要全新的音效频率、并改变嗓音及其他音效来突显宝贝扭曲的视角<ref name="indiesound">{{cite news | last = Desowitz | first = Bill | title = 'Baby Driver': How Edgar Wright's Sound Team Choreographed Squealing Brakes Against Pop Classics | url = https://www.indiewire.com/2017/11/baby-driver-edgar-wright-sound-design-music-1201895451/ | website = IndieWire | date = 2017-11-09 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112025127/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/11/baby-driver-edgar-wright-sound-design-music-1201895451/ | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | access-date = 2021-08-16 }}</ref>。

音效组用八天时间在亚特兰大赛车场录制汽车音效。为录制驾驶员和乘客位置听到的声音（车载录音），录音师吴华生在每辆车安装约六个话筒，进气箱和无线电仪表板各一个，排气口附近两个，发动机舱两个。吊杆操作员詹姆斯·彼得森带着[[麦克风|枪式话筒]]跟在每辆车后录制外部声音，车辆经过的噪音用XY立体声设备录制。剧组在伦敦[[特威克纳姆制片厂|特威克纳姆制片厂]]预先混录音频，最终混音在[[金冠影业|金冠影业]]后期制作设施完成。<ref name="ibc" />

=== 音乐 ===
赖特与普莱斯在电影前期准备阶段交换看法，挑选十首曲目塑造影片音乐走向<ref name="Entcast" />。剧组共取得36首曲目的采用许可，大部分都在电影开拍很久以前写入剧本<ref>{{cite web | title = 'Baby Driver' Director, Crew Prepped to the 'Millisecond' Before Production Began | archive-date = 2021-04-22 | access-date = 2021-08-16 | url = https://variety.com/2018/film/awards/baby-driver-steered-by-choreography-1202707188/ | first = Jon | last = Burlingame | work = Variety | date = 2018-02-22 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210422092559/https://variety.com/2018/film/awards/baby-driver-steered-by-choreography-1202707188/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = The Soundtrack to 'Baby Driver' Is a Music Nerd's Dream – and Director Edgar Wright's | url = https://variety.com/2017/film/news/baby-driver-movie-music-1202482594/ | first = Chris | last = Willman | work = Variety | date = 2017-06-29 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210701003451/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/baby-driver-movie-music-1202482594/ | archive-date = 2021-07-01 }}</ref>。剧本部分[[嘻哈音樂|嘻哈]]或[[電子音樂|电子]]音乐曲目包含听不清的[[取樣_(音樂)|取样]]，赖特无法取得许可<ref name="inspire" /><ref name="exclaim">{{cite web | title = Edgar Wright Explains How Kid Koala and Danger Mouse Shaped the 'Baby Driver' Soundtrack | url = https://exclaim.ca/music/article/edgar_wright_explains_how_kid_koala_and_danger_mouse_shaped_the_baby_driver_soundtrack | first = Matthew | last = Ritchie | work = Exclaim! | date = 2017-06-09 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031024217/http://exclaim.ca/music/article/edgar_wright_explains_how_kid_koala_and_danger_mouse_shaped_the_baby_driver_soundtrack | archive-date = 2020-10-31 | access-date = 2021-08-16 }}</ref>。最后他放弃其中的取样部分，单独取得歌曲许可并纳入[[《极盗车神》电影音乐|配乐唱片]]<ref name="inspire" />。唱片还有《追我呀》和《他反应慢吗》两首原创歌曲，由[[危险老鼠|危险老鼠]]和[[考拉小子|考拉小子]]作曲，其中《追我呀》还有[[Run_the_Jewels|Run the Jewels]]乐队和[[大冯波|大冯波]]的贡献<ref name="lachoreo" />。《他反应慢吗》取样斯派西和博恩瑟的对白，考拉小子用模拟设备制成歌曲<ref>{{cite web | title = Kid Koala talks working on 'Baby Driver' and how he identified with the title character (Interview) | url = https://glidemagazine.com/188069/kid-koala-baby-driver/ | first = Christian | last = Long | work = Glide | date = 2017-06-30 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190706210829/https://glidemagazine.com/188069/kid-koala-baby-driver/ | archive-date = 2019-07-06 | access-date = 2021-08-16 }}</ref>。

2017年6月23日，[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]旗下品牌三十世纪唱片发行本片配乐的[[黑膠唱片|黑胶]]和[[雷射唱片|雷射唱片]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Soundtrack to Baby Driver spans 30 tracks and multiple decades | access-date = 2021-08-16 | url = https://consequence.net/2017/06/soundtrack-to-baby-driver-spans-30-tracks-and-multiple-decades/ | first = Michael | last = Roffman | work = [[前音後果|Consequence of Sound]] | date = 2017-06-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210328122557/https://consequenceofsound.net/2017/06/soundtrack-to-baby-driver-spans-30-tracks-and-multiple-decades/ | archive-date = 2021-03-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2018年4月13日，包含上张唱片未发布内容的《极盗车神第二卷：配乐中的配乐》面世<ref>{{cite web | title = Baby Driver soundtrack gets a sequel featuring new tracks, remixes, and its previously unreleased score | url = https://consequence.net/2018/03/baby-driver-soundtrack-gets-a-sequel/ | first = Randall | last = Colburn | work = Consequence of Sound | date = 2018-03-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225165818/https://consequenceofsound.net/2018/03/baby-driver-soundtrack-gets-a-sequel/ | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。

== 主题 ==
[[File:BabyDriverColorSymbolism.jpg|thumb]]

赖特把宝贝的道德转变视为本片关键主题。大卫·西姆斯在《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]]》杂志发文指出，电影起初以宝贝依赖音乐体现人物道德感与社会脱节，他利用音乐逃避耳鸣症与周围的混乱环境，直到保护黛博拉与约瑟夫的责任感、身边逐渐失控的局面迫使他直面现实。<ref name="atlantic" />电影采用[[黑幫電影|黑幫電影]]常见的表现手法，特别是英雄宿命、彻底的邪恶行径<ref name="nytreview">{{cite web | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/27/movies/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort.html | title = Review: In 'Baby Driver,' It's Kiss Kiss, Zoom Zoom | first = Manohla | last = Dargis | work = The New York Times | date = 2017-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210816172634/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/27/movies/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort.html | archive-date = 2021-08-16 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

与赖特其他电影一样，《极盗车神》色彩动机非常鲜明，以不同颜色象征核心人物性格。宝贝起初衣装颜色单调，反映他眼中的世界只有黑白两色，与其他抢劫犯鲜艳明亮的颜色对比显著：蝙蝠是红色、达琳是紫色与粉色、巴迪为蓝色。随着故事发展，犯罪团伙构成的压力激增，宝贝的服饰色调随之变化，例如浅灰色乃至血迹斑斑的白衬衫。服装设计师考特尼·霍夫曼表示，宝贝浅灰色的服饰代表他竭力抗争，想摆脱犯罪组织。<ref name="color">{{cite web | url = https://nerdist.com/baby-driver-costumes-color-jon-hamm-jaime-foxx-ansel-elgort/ | title = How Baby Driver Reveals Characters Through Colors | first = Kyle | last = Anderson | website = Nerdist | date = 2017-06-01 | archive-date = 2018-12-08 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181208001047/https://nerdist.com/baby-driver-costumes-color-jon-hamm-jaime-foxx-ansel-elgort/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>红色的含义随剧情变化，开始时代表蝙蝠嗜血的一面，到电影后半截变成象征巴迪痛失情侣后的愤怒<ref>{{cite web | url = https://theplaylist.net/color-coding-baby-driver-20171023/ | title = How Edgar Wright's 'Baby Driver' Color Codes Its Characters | first = Julia | last = Teti | website = The Playlist | date = 2017-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200225154356/https://theplaylist.net/color-coding-baby-driver-20171023/ | archive-date = 2020-02-25 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》刊登[[贾斯汀·张|贾斯汀·张]]的评论，称《极盗车神》探索身份认同与个人风格，同时探讨两者如何决定人的社会地位<ref name="latreview">{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-08-10 | url = https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-baby-driver-review-20170627-story.html | title = Edgar Wright's exuberant 'Baby Driver' is an automotive musical like no other | first = Justin | last = Chang | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2017-06-27 | access-date = 2021-08-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210810202910/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-baby-driver-review-20170627-story.html }}</ref>。

大卫·霍林希德与简·胡在《[[洛杉矶书评|洛杉矶书评]]》发文，认为种族也是本片重要主题。文章以电影多个角度着手，如选角着眼“白人就是纯真”立场，建立“种族意识”潜台词，又如[[文化挪用|文化挪用]]的伦理道德问题。<ref name="labook">{{cite web | url = https://avidly.lareviewofbooks.org/2017/07/26/oh-hell-yeah-baby-le-chauffeur/ | title = Oh Hell Yeah Baby, Le Chauffeur | first1 = David | last1 = Hollingshead | first2 = Jane | last2 = Hu | work = Los Angeles Review of Books | date = 2017-07-26 | archive-date = 2021-06-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210603055438/https://avidly.lareviewofbooks.org/2017/07/26/oh-hell-yeah-baby-le-chauffeur/ | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>

