月中旬在北美和英国上映<ref name="initialsch">{{cite news | last = Stedman | first = Alex | title = Edgar Wright's 'Baby Driver' Moves Up Nearly Two Months to June | archive-date = 2021-02-05 | dead-url = no | url = https://variety.com/2017/film/news/baby-driver-release-date-moved-up-edgar-wright-1202017531/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210205172451/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/baby-driver-release-date-moved-up-edgar-wright-1202017531/ | access-date = 2021-08-17 | work = Variety | date = 2017-03-27 }}</ref>，但影片在电影节巡演反响热烈<ref name="thrtristar">{{cite web | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/tristar-chief-hannah-minghella-wonder-woman-envy-baby-driver-buzz-her-late-fathers-legacy-1014814/ | title = TriStar Chief Hannah Minghella on 'Wonder Woman' Envy, 'Baby Driver' Buzz and Her Late Father's Legacy | first = Tatiana | last = Siegel | date = 2017-06-26 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-date = 2021-07-14 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210714005538/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/tristar-chief-hannah-minghella-wonder-woman-envy-baby-driver-buzz-her-late-fathers-legacy-1014814/ }}</ref><ref name="srus">{{cite web | url = https://screenrant.com/baby-driver-box-office-success/2/ | title = Is Edgar Wright's Baby Driver A Box Office Hit? | first = Zak | last = Wojnar | website = [[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]] | date = 2017-07-20 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210803022721/https://screenrant.com/baby-driver-box-office-success/2/ | archive-date = 2021-08-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，两家公司决定提前六周、在6月28日上映<ref>{{cite web | last = Gettell | first = Oliver | title = Baby Driver release date moves up to June | url = https://ew.com/movies/2017/03/27/baby-driver-release-date-moves-up/ | date = 2017-03-27 | work = Entertainment Weekly | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210730174203/https://ew.com/movies/2017/03/27/baby-driver-release-date-moves-up/ | archive-date = 2021-07-30 }}</ref>。通常暑期电影市场早期竞争更激烈，小成本电影更适合排在后期，故此次提前很不寻常<ref name="initialsch" /><ref name="thrtristar" />。

