//www.the-numbers.com/home-market/packaged-media-sales-chart/2017/10/15 | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。截至2018年1月，电影的DVD和蓝光影碟共售出59万5111份<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Baby-Driver#tab=video-sales | title = Baby Driver – Video Sales | website = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210507101725/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Baby-Driver#tab=video-sales | archive-date = 2021-05-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

