== 反响 ==
=== 票房 ===
《极盗车神》在中国市场表现一般，北美和欧洲上映期间反响上佳，属票房大片<ref name="srus" /><ref>{{cite web | title = China Box Office: 'Valerian' Notches Modest $29M Win, While 'Cars 3' and 'Baby Driver' Sputter | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/china-box-office-valerian-notches-modest-29m-win-cars-3-baby-driver-sputter-1033286/ | first = Patrick | last = Brzeski | date = 2017-08-28 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207223108/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/china-box-office-valerian-notches-modest-29m-win-cars-3-baby-driver-sputter-1033286 }}</ref><ref name="Ukbo">{{cite web | dead-url = no | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/jul/04/uk-box-office-despicable-me-3-baby-driver-transformers-the-last-knight | title = Despicable Me 3 overtakes Transformers and Baby Driver at UK box office | first = Charles | last = Grant | work = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2017-07-04 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201027062454/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/jul/04/uk-box-office-despicable-me-3-baby-driver-transformers-the-last-knight | archive-date = 2020-10-27 }}</ref>。电影在美国和加拿大收入约1.08亿美元，其他市场1.19亿，总票房约2.27亿<ref name="BOM" />，在2017年电影排第43<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210524195248/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/world/2017/ | dead-url = no | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/world/2017/ | title = 2017 Worldwide Box Office | website = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-date = 2021-05-24 }}</ref>，创下赖特导演电影新高<ref name="dprofit" />。扣除拍摄预算、营销成本及其他费用，三星与传媒权利资本净获利5150万美元<ref name="dprofit">{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2018/03/movie-profit-2017-baby-driver-wonder-split-annabelle-creation-girls-trip-1202354131/ | title = Small Movies, Big Profits: 2017 Most Valuable Blockbuster Tournament | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2018-03-29 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210514014924/https://deadline.com/2018/03/movie-profit-2017-baby-driver-wonder-split-annabelle-creation-girls-trip-1202354131/ | archive-date = 2021-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。良好口碑与系列大片票房号召刀减弱是本片大卖的重要原因<ref name="Entcast" /><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/box-office-hollywoods-franchise-crisis-worsens-july-fourth-1018493/ | title = Box Office: Hollywood's Franchise Crisis Worsens Over July Fourth | first = Pamela | last = McClintock | date = 2017-07-03 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207210924/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-hollywoods-franchise-crisis-worsens-july-fourth-1018493 | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

美国电影院出口民调数据表明，本片在各类观众都有很大商业潜力。电影首映当晚的[[影院评分|影院评分]]民调显示影迷平均评分“A−”（最高“A+”，最低“F”）。观众以年轻人为主，五成二不超过25岁，五成七为男子。观众选择本片的主要原因包括：想看动作片（四成四）、喜欢片中演员（两成六）、喜欢导演（一成六）。按小时计算的预售票量令《[[变形金刚5：最后的骑士|变形金刚5：最后的骑士]]》黯然失色。<ref name="bdwide">{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2017/06/baby-driver-opening-day-box-office-1202121299/ | title = 'Baby Driver' Dings 'Transformers' For Thursday Top Spot With $3.3M; 'Wonder Woman' Whips 'Batman V. Superman' | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2017-06-30 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207214448/https://deadline.com/2017/06/baby-driver-opening-day-box-office-1202121299/ | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>即便考虑媒体好评与良好口碑，大部分经济型电影也难以像本片这样在竞争激烈的市场长时间卖座<ref name="preview" /><ref name="bdwide" />。《极盗车神》全面上映第一天收入570万美元，其中包括星期二晚预映进账210万美元，随后又在周四拿下330万美元<ref name="opening">{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2017/06/baby-driver-opening-day-box-office-1202121299/ | title = 'Baby Driver' Dings 'Transformers' For Thursday Top Spot With $3.3M; 'Wonder Woman' Whips 'Batman V. Superman' | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2017-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207214448/https://deadline.com/2017/06/baby-driver-opening-day-box-office-1202121299/ | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。影片首周末共在3226家电影院收入近三千万美元排名第二，仅次于《[[神偷奶爸3|神偷奶爸3]]》<ref name="Boperformance">{{cite news | last = Kelley | first = Seth | title = Box Office: 'Despicable Me 3' Rules, 'Baby Driver' Shows Strong, Will Ferrell's 'House' Collapses | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | work = Variety | dead-url = no | url = https://variety.com/2017/film/news/box-office-despicable-me-3-baby-driver-the-house-4-1202486134/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207212847/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/box-office-despicable-me-3-baby-driver-the-house-4-1202486134/ | date = 2017-07-02 }}</ref>，超出索尼的首周票房预期<ref name="bdwide" />，创下赖特导演电影在美国开映的新纪录<ref name="Boperformance" /><ref name="opening2">{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2017/07/despicable-me-3-baby-driver-the-house-july-4th-weekend-box-office-independence-day-1202122599/ | title = 'Baby Driver' Speeds To $27M+; Ferrell & Poehler's 'House' Burns Down As 'Despicable Me 3' Dominates | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2017-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210619214038/https://deadline.com/2017/07/despicable-me-3-baby-driver-the-house-july-4th-weekend-box-office-independence-day-1202122599/ | archive-date = 2021-06-19 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。第二个周末本片票房降至1300万美元，只有首周三成七<ref>{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2017/07/spider-man-homecoming-box-office-opening-1202124834/ | title = 'Spider-Man: Homecoming' Still Swinging In As Sony's Second Best Domestic Opening Ever With $116M–$118M | last = D'Alessandro | first = Anthony | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2017-07-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210619074949/https://deadline.com/2017/07/spider-man-homecoming-box-office-opening-1202124834/ | archive-date = 2021-06-19 | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>；第三个周末电影进账880万美元<ref>{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2017/07/war-for-the-planet-of-the-apes-spiderman-homecoming-box-office-weekend-1202128838/ | title = 'War For The Planet Of The Apes' Loots $56.5M In Box Office Spoils | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | website = Deadline Hollywood | date = 2017-07-16 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210618081855/https://deadline.com/2017/07/war-for-the-planet-of-the-apes-spiderman-homecoming-box-office-weekend-1202128838/ | archive-date = 2021-06-18 }}</ref>。8月14日，电影在美国市场收入破亿<ref>{{cite news | last = McNary | first = Dave | title = 'Baby Driver' Crosses $100 Million Milestone at Domestic Box Office | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | dead-url = no | date = 2017-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207220307/https://variety.com/2017/film/festivals/baby-driver-domestic-box-office-1202526701/ | url = https://variety.com/2017/film/festivals/baby-driver-domestic-box-office-1202526701/ | access-date = 2021-08-17 | work = Variety }}</ref>。三星在8月25日这周扩大影片上映院线范围，从1074家电影院收入120万美元，比上周增加三成四<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-06-19 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210619000543/https://deadline.com/2017/08/hitmans-bodyguard-birth-of-the-dragon-leap-all-saints-low-summer-box-office-weekend-mayweather-mcgregor-fight-1202156230/ | date = 2017-08-25 | url = https://deadline.com/2017/08/hitmans-bodyguard-birth-of-the-dragon-leap-all-saints-low-summer-box-office-weekend-mayweather-mcgregor-fight-1202156230/ | title = The Hitman's Bodyguard' Tries To Deflect Hurricane Harvey & Mayweather-McGregor | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | website = Deadline Hollywood | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。2017年10月19日，《极盗车神》撤下北美院线<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl1165854209/ | title = Baby Driver - Domestic Release | website = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210803221712/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl1165854209/ | archive-date = 2021-08-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

