美国传媒把《极盗车神》评为2017年度佳片<ref name="best2017">{{cite news | title = Best of 2017: Film Critic Top Ten Lists | website = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | first = Jason | last = Dietz | date = 2017-12-05 | archive-date = 2021-05-03 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-17 | url = https://www.metacritic.com/feature/best-movies-of-2017 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210503113314/https://www.metacritic.com/feature/best-movies-of-2017 }}</ref>，如[[國家評論協會|國家評論協會]]的[[国家评论协会年度十大佳片|年度十大佳片]]<ref>{{cite news | title = National Board of Review Announces 2017 Award Winners | website = [[國家評論協會|National Board of Review]] | first = Jason | last = Dietz | url = https://nationalboardofreview.org/2017/11/national-board-review-announces-2017-award-winners/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210507024807/https://nationalboardofreview.org/2017/11/national-board-review-announces-2017-award-winners/ | archive-date = 2021-05-07 | dead-url = no | date = 2017-11-28 | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。新闻工作者称赞影片制作精良，尽显导演专长<ref name="nytreview" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Film Review: Baby Driver | url = https://consequence.net/2017/06/film-review-baby-driver/ | first = Michael | last = Roffman | work = Consequence of Sound | date = 2017-06-26 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210816160445/https://consequence.net/2017/06/film-review-baby-driver/ | archive-date = 2021-08-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = In 'Baby Driver,' The Action, The Script And The Music Go Full Throttle | url = https://www.npr.org/2017/06/27/533965743/in-baby-driver-the-action-the-script-and-the-music-go-full-throttle | first = Chris | last = Klimek | website = [[全国公共广播电台|NPR]] | date = 2017-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201023121912/https://www.npr.org/2017/06/27/533965743/in-baby-driver-the-action-the-script-and-the-music-go-full-throttle | archive-date = 2020-10-23 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》的特里·怀特称本片“原创程度多年来少有”，是“银幕上最接近追车歌剧”的作品<ref name="empirereview">{{cite web | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/baby-driver-review/ | title = Baby Driver Review | first = Terri | last = White | date = 2017-06-19 | work = Empire | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512165419/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/baby-driver-review/ | archive-date = 2021-05-12 }}</ref>。[[彼得·布拉德肖|彼得·布拉德肖]]在《[[衛報|衛報]]》发文称赞电影既时尚又迷人，“充满纯粹的快乐与善良本质”，坚持追车没有人受害所以不是犯罪的浪漫理念<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/jun/27/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort-kevin-spacey-jon-hamm-jamie-foxx | title = Baby Driver review – Edgar Wright puts pedal to the metal for wildly enjoyable heist caper | first = Peter | last = Bradshaw | date = 2017-06-27 | work = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | location = London, England | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210717080107/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/jun/27/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort-kevin-spacey-jon-hamm-jamie-foxx | archive-date = 2021-07-17 }}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》刊登彼得·德布鲁格的文章，赞扬影片凭“高明的笑点、突然的反转……恰如其分的歌曲”，结合特别突出的追车场面自成一派<ref name="varietyreview">{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2017/film/reviews/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-1202006730/ | title = SXSW Film Review: 'Baby Driver' | first = Peter | last = Debruge | date = 2017-03-12 | work = Variety | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200810030202/https://variety.com/2017/film/reviews/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-1202006730/ | archive-date = 2020-08-10 }}</ref>。

影评人高度评价演员表现<ref name="nytreview" /><ref name="cst">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-08-17 | url = https://chicago.suntimes.com/2017/6/27/18373077/baby-driver-a-high-speed-vehicle-for-the-fast-and-the-hilarious | title = 'Baby Driver' a high speed vehicle for the fast and the hilarious | first = Richard | last = Roeper | work = [[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] | publisher = Sun-Times Media Group | date = 2017-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015355/https://chicago.suntimes.com/2017/6/27/18373077/baby-driver-a-high-speed-vehicle-for-the-fast-and-the-hilarious | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，特别是艾尔高特和詹姆斯<ref name="latreview" /><ref name="av">{{cite web | url = https://www.avclub.com/edgar-wright-drifts-out-of-comedy-and-into-the-crime-mu-1798191825 | title = Edgar Wright drifts out of comedy and into the crime-musical bliss of Baby Driver | first = A.A. | last = Dowd | work = [[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]] | date = 2017-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210629121510/https://www.avclub.com/edgar-wright-drifts-out-of-comedy-and-into-the-crime-mu-1798191825 | archive-date = 2021-06-29 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="vox">{{cite web | url = https://www.vox.com/culture/2017/6/27/15874888/baby-driver-review | title = Edgar Wright's wildly entertaining Baby Driver is a lean, mean, genre-smashing machine | first = Genevieve | last = Koski | work = [[Vox|Vox]] | date = 2017-07-01 | archive-date = 2021-04-20 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210420190958/https://www.vox.com/culture/2017/6/27/15874888/baby-driver-review }}</ref>。文章认为前者足以成为大明星，詹姆斯的表现“光芒四射”<ref name="slant">{{cite web | url = https://www.slantmagazine.com/film/baby-driver/ | title = Baby Driver | first = Jake | last = Cole | work = [[偏锋杂志|Slant Magazine]] | date = 2017-06-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201030030019/https://www.slantmagazine.com/film/baby-driver/ | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-10-30 | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref><ref name="time">{{cite web | url = https://time.com/4835390/review-baby-driver-ansel-elgort/ | title = Baby Driver Is Fast, Furious and Full of Heart | first = Stephanie | last = Zacharek | work = [[時代雜誌|Time]] | date = 2017-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210410152006/https://time.com/4835390/review-baby-driver-ansel-elgort/ | archive-date = 2021-04-10 | access-date = 2021-04-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。影评人对电影人物塑造看法不一，有些批评片中部分人物、特别是女人的形象<ref name="paste">{{cite web | url = https://www.pastemagazine.com/movies/baby-driver/baby-driver/ | title = Baby Driver | first = Will | last = Leitch | work = Paste | date = 2017-06-25 | archive-date = 2021-02-26 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210226073543/https://www.pastemagazine.com/movies/baby-driver/baby-driver/ | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.popsugar.com/entertainment/Problem-Baby-Driver-43753525 | title = The Disappointing Reason Baby Driver Doesn't Live Up to the Hype | first = Sarah | last = Siegel | website = PopSugar | date = 2017-07-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200629104657/https://www.popsugar.com/entertainment/Problem-Baby-Driver-43753525 | archive-date = 2020-06-29 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。“[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]”的埃里克·科恩指出，黛博拉的人物发展有欠成熟<ref name="indiereview">{{cite news | last = Kohn | first = Eric | title = 'Baby Driver' Review: Edgar Wright's Brilliant Car Chase Musical Casts Ansel Elgort As an Outlaw Fred Astaire – SXSW 2017 | url = https://www.indiewire.com/2017/03/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort-jon-hamm-sxsw-2017-1201792735/ | website = IndieWire | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | location = Los Angeles, California | date = 2017-03-12 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210228063643/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/03/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort-jon-hamm-sxsw-2017-1201792735/ | archive-date = 2021-02-28 | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>；怀特也觉得她的背景交待不足，人物缺乏深度与自我<ref name="empirereview" />。理查德·布罗迪在《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》发文，认为本片几乎每句对白都有目的，缺乏不同人物间的细微差异，演员种族多样但角色很大程度上可以互换<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.newyorker.com/culture/richard-brody/baby-driver-an-artificially-sweetened-hollywood-heist-film | title = "Baby Driver," an Artificially Sweetened Hollywood Heist Film | first = Richard | last = Brody | date = 2017-07-03 | work = [[紐約客|The New Yorker]] | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210226052937/https://www.newyorker.com/culture/richard-brody/baby-driver-an-artificially-sweetened-hollywood-heist-film | archive-date = 2021-02-26 }}</ref>。《[[紐約_(雜誌)|纽约]]》杂志刊登大卫·艾德尔斯汀的文章，观点同《[[纽约观察家报|纽约观察家报]]》的塞尔玛·亚当斯类似，认为人物发展是本片优势所在<ref name="nymag">{{cite web | url = https://www.vulture.com/2017/06/baby-driver-movie-review.html | title = Edgar Wright's Baby Driver Is a Cinematic Joyride | first = David | last = Edelstein | work = [[紐約_(雜誌)|New York]] | publisher = [[紐約市的媒體|New York Media]] | location = New York City | date = 2017-06-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210508124127/https://www.vulture.com/2017/06/baby-driver-movie-review.html | archive-date = 2021-05-08 | access-date = 2021-05-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="observer">{{cite web | url = https://observer.com/2017/06/heist-movie-baby-driver-steals-summer/ | title = Heist Movie 'Baby Driver' Steals Summer | first = Thelma | last = Adams | work = [[纽约观察家报|Observer]] | publisher = Observer Media | location = New York City | date = 2017-06-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210118205401/https://observer.com/2017/06/heist-movie-baby-driver-steals-summer/ | archive-date = 2021-01-18 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

电影高潮桥段的剧本创作和情节发展引起反弹<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.cnn.com/2017/06/27/entertainment/baby-driver-review/index.html | title = 'Baby Driver' clicks on all cylinders | first = Brian | last = Lowry | date = 2017-06-28 | website = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | publisher = [[透納廣播公司|Turner Broadcasting Systems]] | location = Atlanta, Georgia | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111215822/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/06/27/entertainment/baby-driver-review/index.html }}</ref>。影评人认为高潮部分基调变化太大太快，破坏观影体验，是本片最大的败笔<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.detroitnews.com/story/entertainment/movies/2017/06/27/movie-review-baby-driver-spins-circles/103230460/ | title = Review: High-style 'Baby Driver' spins in circles | first = Adam | last = Graham | date = 2017-06-27 | work = The Detroit News | publisher = Gary Miles | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-06-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200629104710/https://www.detroitnews.com/story/entertainment/movies/2017/06/27/movie-review-baby-driver-spins-circles/103230460/ | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref><ref name="paste" />。亚当·奈曼在《[[影迷_(杂志)|影迷]]》杂志宣称，剧本失误表明赖特独自编剧的经验不足<ref name="cine">{{cite web | url = https://www.cineaste.com/fall2017/baby-driver/ | title = Baby Driver (Web Exclusive) | first = Adam | last = Nayman | work = Cineaste | date = Fall 2017 | archive-date = 2021-08-07 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210807232525/https://www.cineaste.com/fall2017/baby-driver | dead-url = no }}</ref>，“[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]”网站认为《极盗车神》的势头在高潮桥段损失殆尽，很不协调而且很不寻常，“难得见到电影人开场表现如此亮眼，最后却草草收场”<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | url = https://www.thewrap.com/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort/ | title = 'Baby Driver' Review: Edgar Wright Floors It Before Driving Off a Cliff | first = Sam | last = Frogoso | date = 2017-06-27 | work = [[TheWrap|TheWrap]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210303035031/https://www.thewrap.com/baby-driver-review-edgar-wright-ansel-elgort/ | archive-date = 2021-03-03 | access-date = 2021-08-17 }}</ref>。《纽约客》刊登安东尼·莱恩的文章，觉得本片太自命不凡，不像《[[終棘警探|終棘警探]]》（2007年）等赖特动作喜剧更有自知之明<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2017/07/03/baby-driver-and-my-journey-through-french-cinema | title = "Baby Driver" and "My Journey Through French Cinema" | first = Anthony | last = Lane | date = 2017-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210304153239/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2017/07/03/baby-driver-and-my-journey-through-french-cinema | archive-date = 2021-03-04 | access-date = 2021-08-17 | work = The New Yorker | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]网站收集本片394篇评论，认可度达九成二。网站的共识评述写道：“风格时尚、激动人心，再用所向披靡的配乐推波助澜。《极盗车神》急速上路——证明创作快节奏的动作片无需牺牲惊悚元素。”<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/baby_driver | title = Baby Driver | access-date = 2021-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210815092350/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/baby_driver | archive-date = 2021-08-15 | dead-url = no | publisher = [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] }}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]共收集影片53篇评论，[[加權平均數|加权平均分]]86（最高100），代表“普遍好评”<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.metacritic.com/movie/baby-driver | title = Baby Driver | access-date = 2021-08-17 | publisher = Metacritic | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210728035040/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/baby-driver | archive-date = 2021-07-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

