== 续集构想 ==
《极盗车神》大卖促使制片商有意拍续集。2017年12月赖特宣布有意创作剧本<ref name="Entcast" /><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.slashfilm.com/baby-driver-sequel-2/ | title = 'Baby Driver' Sequel "Being Hammered Out," Edgar Wright Plans to Write the Screenplay | last = Hall | first = Jacob | website = /Film | date = 2017-12-05 | access-date = 2021-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210410145010/https://www.slashfilm.com/baby-driver-sequel-2/ | archive-date = 2021-04-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，2019年1月开始写作，加入大批新角色推动情节发展<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/edgar-wright-next-film-psychological-horror-plus-baby-driver-2-update-exclusive/ | title = Edgar Wright's Next Film Is A Psychological Horror, Plus Baby Driver 2 Update – Exclusive | first1 = Ben | last1 = Travis | first2 = John | last2 = Nugent | work = Empire | date = 2019-01-21 | access-date = 2021-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210523160506/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/edgar-wright-next-film-psychological-horror-plus-baby-driver-2-update-exclusive/ | archive-date = 2021-05-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。同年七月，赖特已将完成的剧本拿给艾尔高特，片名尚不确定<ref>{{cite web | url = https://collider.com/baby-driver-2-update/ | title = Ansel Elgort and Edgar Wright Tease 'Baby Driver 2' Likely Happening Soon | first = Adam | last = Chitwood | website = Collider | date = 2019-07-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112033643/https://collider.com/baby-driver-2-update/ | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-18 }}</ref>。2021年1月，赖特确认完成续集剧本<ref>{{Cite web | last = Aubrey | first = Elizabeth | date = 2021-01-30 | title = Edgar Wright confirms 'Baby Driver 2' script is complete | url = https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/film/edgar-wright-confirms-baby-driver-2-script-is-complete-2869073 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210208180038/https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/film/edgar-wright-confirms-baby-driver-2-script-is-complete-2869073 | archive-date = 2021-02-08 | access-date = 2021-08-18 | website = NME }}</ref>。

